From: Armbian
Subject: orangepi-zero-plus: MACPWR (eth PHY power) + SPL SPI boot

Carried over from the v2024.01-era board patch, rebased onto v2026.07-rc4's
orangepi_zero_plus_defconfig. MACPWR=PD6 powers the on-board ethernet PHY (needed
for u-boot network/PXE), and SPL_SPI_SUNXI enables booting from the SPI flash.
Neither is in the upstream defconfig.

--- a/configs/orangepi_zero_plus_defconfig
+++ b/configs/orangepi_zero_plus_defconfig
@@ -12,3 +12,5 @@
 CONFIG_SUN8I_EMAC=y
 CONFIG_USB_EHCI_HCD=y
 CONFIG_USB_OHCI_HCD=y
+CONFIG_MACPWR="PD6"
+CONFIG_SPL_SPI_SUNXI=y
